@node ax_split_version
@unnumberedsec ax_split_version

@majorheading Synopsis

@smallexample
AX_SPLIT_VERSION
@end smallexample

@majorheading Description

Splits a version number in the format MAJOR.MINOR.POINT into its
separate components.

Sets the variables.

